"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:2.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.6</span> 标题：投枪、标枪、短枪（javelin）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：כִּידוֹן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kidon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:18\">JOS 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:18\">JOS 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:26\">JOS 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:6\">1SA 17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:45\">1SA 17:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:23\">JOB 39:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:21\">JOB 41:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:23\">JER 6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:42\">JER 50:42</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：שִׁרְיָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：shiryah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:18\">JOB 41:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ὕσσος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：hussos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:29\">JHN 19:29</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0955_javelin.jpg\" alt=\"用于狩猎和战斗的标枪或长矛\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">用于狩猎和战斗的标枪或长矛 (© Unknown - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>投枪是一种短矛或大箭（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.14.2 箭 (arrow)&lt;REALIA:2.14.2&gt;</a> ），比枪轻一些，适合投掷。持枪的人可以站立着，或骑在马上，或在战车上，向敌人投掷。投枪的杆用木头或芦苇制成。和长枪一样，投枪也带有一个金属尖头，固定方式也和固定枪头相同（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.5.1 枪头 (spearhead)&lt;REALIA:2.5.1&gt;</a> ）。投枪枪杆的中间位置通常缠着一根绳子，并套在抛掷者的手指上。投枪掷出后，绳子松开使投枪旋转，从而飞行更加稳定、准确，而且飞得更远。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>“投枪”可以翻译为“投掷的枪”或“轻巧的枪”。</p>\n<p>罗兰‧沃克斯（Roland de Vaux）提出，希伯来文<em>kidon</em> 是指一种长剑或弯刀。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 在上列一些经文中采纳了这种解释。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:21\">JOB 41:21</a> （《和》41:29）中译作“sabre”（“弯刀”），但<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:26\">JOS 8:26</a> 把这种武器翻译成小很多的“dagger”（“匕首”）。不过，大部分译本都译作“投枪”、“枪”或“长矛”。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:18\">JOB 41:18</a> （《和》41:26）中，希伯来文<em>shiryah</em> 是指一种武器，但具体所指不详。许多译本将这个词译为“投枪、标枪”（“javelin”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、《和》、《和修》），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 作“lance”（“长矛”），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Living Translation\">NLT</abbr> 译成“pointed shaft”（“尖头杆”）。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:29\">JHN 19:29</a> ，希腊文<em>hussos</em> 是一个异文，有些学者接受这个异文，而不接受证据更加有力的<em>hussōpos</em> （“牛膝草”），但大部分学者拒绝这个异文。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
